Package org.odpi.openmetadata.adminservices.configuration.properties

Class EngineServiceConfig

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.adminservices.configuration.properties.AdminServicesConfigHeader
org.odpi.openmetadata.adminservices.configuration.properties.OMAGServerClientConfig
org.odpi.openmetadata.adminservices.configuration.properties.EngineServiceConfig
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class EngineServiceConfig extends OMAGServerClientConfig
EngineServiceConfig provides the properties to configure a single engine service in an engine hosting server. The engine service runs one or more engines of a specific type. The configuration for each of these engines is extracted from the partner OMAS using the engine name as the qualified name.
